<span id="freeTextContainer17539671906050865613">The stories were very good but I had a hard time following along...there wasn&apos;t a lot of detail but I guess most of the people he interviewed didn&apos;t want to be in the spotlight. I never saw his spots on the Today Show but think I may have enjoyed watching them better than reading about them. It still was very inspiring and nice to read about these extraordinary people and how they help others! </span>
